  "install_text": "Bring instant BLE visibility to any site with Lansitec’s pocket-sized Compact Bluetooth Gateway. The slim 95.4* 61.4*7.3 mm bridge captures iBeacon, Eddystone, or custom sensor frames and backhauls them over global NB-IoT / LTE-M bands. A 600 mAh rechargeable battery keeps data flowing for ≈ 10 h without mains power, while AES-128 security and smart edge filtering make it a dependable, grab-and-go solution for mobile, pop-up, or emergency deployments.",
